timing_library...ccs_noise_data(25.10)  timing_library...ccs_noise_data(25.10)

Name
       timing_library_read_ccs_noise_data

Syntax
       timing_library_read_ccs_noise_data

       {true | false}

       Default: true

       Allows CCS noise constructs to be read from a library.

       This  global  variable  can be used when the CCS library contains noise
       models, and SI glitch analysis is being performed.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

